	<div class="title"><h1>淡马锡概览</h1>
</div>

	<div class="par parsys"><div class="text parbase section">



<div class="intro"><p>淡马锡是总部位于新加坡的国际投资公司。作为跨世代的投资者，我们放眼未来，努力开拓创新。&nbsp;</p>
</div>


</div>
<div class="video-inline parbase section">

    <div class="video-wrapper">
        <video id="brightcove-808656" class="video-brightcove video-js"
            data-video-id="5655948331001"
            data-account="4922155157001"
            data-player="ryFCfJxS"
            data-embed="default"
            data-application-id=""
            
            
            controls="controls">
        </video>
        <div class="inline-video-overlay-text">
            
        </div>
    </div>
<script src="https://localhost:8087/etc.clientlibs/temasek-commons/clientlibs/common/video-brightcove.min.js"></script>


</div>
<div class="parsys_column column_3"><div class="parsys_column column_3-c0"><div class="statistic parbase section">
<div class="statistic    charcoal-bg no-image " data-goto-section="#null">

    <figure class="statistic">
        <span class="statistic-figure"><span class="statistic-figure-inner"><span class="statistic-number">1974</span>年</span></span>
        <figcaption class="statistic-label">
        	<p>淡马锡成立</p>

        </figcaption>
    </figure>


</div></div>
</div><div class="parsys_column column_3-c1"><div class="statistic parbase section">
<div class="statistic    purple-bg animate countUp no-image " data-goto-section="#null">

    <figure class="statistic">
        <span class="statistic-figure"><span class="statistic-figure-inner"><span class="statistic-number" data-count="13">0</span>个</span></span>
        <figcaption class="statistic-label">
        	<p>办事处分布在9个国家</p>

        </figcaption>
    </figure>


</div></div>
</div><div class="parsys_column column_3-c2"><div class="statistic parbase section">
<div class="statistic    blue-bg animate countUp no-image " data-goto-section="#null">

    <figure class="statistic">
        <span class="statistic-figure"><span class="statistic-figure-inner"><span class="statistic-number" data-count="4">0</span>,<span class="statistic-number" data-count="340">0</span>亿新元</span></span>
        <figcaption class="statistic-label">
        	<p>截至2025年3月31日的<br>
投资组合净值&nbsp;</p>

        </figcaption>
    </figure>


</div></div>
</div></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div class="text parbase section">



<div class="default"><p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>我们以<a href="our-purpose-charter-values">淡马锡的使命、淡马锡宪章和价值观</a>为指导，遵循商业原则运营，致力于实现长期可持续的回报。</p>
</div>


</div>
<div class="parsys_column column_1"><div class="parsys_column column_1-c0"><div class="statistic parbase section">
<div class="statistic    green-bg no-image " data-goto-section="#null">

    <figure class="statistic">
        <span class="statistic-figure"><span class="statistic-figure-inner">延延世代，欣欣向荣 </span></span>
        <figcaption class="statistic-label">
        	<p>放眼未来，我们追求卓越，践行使命，造福世代</p>

        </figcaption>
    </figure>


</div></div>
</div></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div class="text parbase section">



<div class="default"><p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>我们长期持有<a></a>投资组合，而且依据资产负债表进行投资，所以不受限于“资金有效期”。我们主要进行股权投资。我们不会对资产类别、所在国、行业或单一企业设置投资目标。我们的投资活动由淡马锡长期<a href="../our-investments/investment-approach">结构性趋势</a>为引导。<br>
</p>
</div>


</div>
<div class="parsys_column column_4"><div class="parsys_column column_4-c0"><div class="image parbase section">



    <figure id="cq-image-jsp-/content/temasek-corporate/zh/about-us/temasek-at-a-glance/jcr:content/par/image" class="img-width-100 default image" data-tooltip-content="null">

<img src="https://localhost:8087/content/dam/temasek-corporate/about-us/corporate-profile/Digitisation%20Icon_RGB.png" alt=" " style="display: block;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;" title=" " class="cq-dd-image">

        <figcaption class="image-caption">
        	<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="border-bottom: 1.0px dotted; color: rgb(21,175,155);" class="tooltip" title="跨行业数字科技" data-content="{&quot;description&quot;:&quot;跨行业数字科技&quot;}"><b>数字化进程</b></span></p>

        </figcaption>

    </figure></div>
</div><div class="parsys_column column_4-c1"><div class="image parbase section">



    <figure id="cq-image-jsp-/content/temasek-corporate/zh/about-us/temasek-at-a-glance/jcr:content/par/image_616037652" class="img-width-100 default image" data-tooltip-content="null">

